<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I teach sixth grade and I think a better choice for the age and a better written book is Healing Water by Joyce Moyer Hostetter. It&apos;s YA and an histor<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I teach sixth grade and I think a better choice for the age and a better written book is Healing Water by Joyce Moyer Hostetter. It's YA and an historical fiction novel about Molokai and the leper colony. All my students who read it, enjoy it.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
