    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Karen by: </span>
      Minooka Bookies
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2643889-karen?shelf=my-5-star-reads">my-5-star-reads</a>
